                        <seg type="trans" xml:id="s01_trans">May 28, 1926.</seg>
                        <seg type="trans" xml:id="s02_trans">The family of Tse:ghw(i)s(i) (Jeff
                            Tindle) lost a small child this morning<pc>.</pc></seg>
                        <seg type="trans" xml:id="s03_trans">It will be buried tomorrow in Echota
                            Cemetery, and you diggers must make preparation.</seg>
                    </ab>
